metadata.name: Hisato Cyberpunk Samurai - DDD
metadata.description:
DenDekaDen Dedication Painting (Fan Art) Contest Entries

I drew HISATO, one of DenDekaDen's characters, as a cyberpunk samurai and a flame wielder. The mysterious and mysterious part of the character is expressed through the use of shadows.

We hope that DenDekaDen will be more exciting.
